{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-yuzao-010__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-yuzao-010", "source_id": "xiaoya-yuzao-010__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·010.1", "text_original": "緜蠻黃鳥，止于丘阿。道之云遠，我勞如何！\n飲之食之，教之誨之。命彼後車，謂之載之。", "text_normalized": "緜蠻黃鳥，止于丘阿。道之云遠，我勞如何！\n飲之食之，教之誨之。命彼後車，謂之載之。", "notes": "緜蠻 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-yuzao-010__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-yuzao-010", "source_id": "xiaoya-yuzao-010__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·010.2", "text_original": "緜蠻黃鳥，止于丘隅。豈敢憚行？畏不能趨。\n飲之食之，教之誨之。命彼後車，謂之載之。", "text_normalized": "緜蠻黃鳥，止于丘隅。豈敢憚行？畏不能趨。\n飲之食之，教之誨之。命彼後車，謂之載之。", "notes": "緜蠻 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-yuzao-010__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-yuzao-010", "source_id": "xiaoya-yuzao-010__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·010.3", "text_original": "緜蠻黃鳥，止于丘側。豈敢憚行，畏不能極。\n飲之食之，教之誨之。命彼後車，謂之載之。", "text_normalized": "緜蠻黃鳥，止于丘側。豈敢憚行，畏不能極。\n飲之食之，教之誨之。命彼後車，謂之載之。", "notes": "緜蠻 Chinese stanza 3."}
